      • readLine

        public java.lang.String readLine(java.lang.String prompt)
        This is a dual purpose function. It both allows the user to get a string input, as well as, get the next input for all other readers. In all cases, it will return the next input as a string, either to the user or another reader.
        Parameters:
        prompt - String prompt to show user
        Returns:
        inputed string
